data.description:
No electric payment sounds great, right? Save hundreds with these solar panels. This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom East side home. As you step inside, you'll find a spacious living area with an open-concept layout that allows for versatile use of space, making it an ideal candidate for your customization and design ideas. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and offers a great space for your culinary aspirations.

It's a wonderful place to enjoy the warm El Paso weather and make lasting memories with family and friends.

Don't miss out, call today to see it.
